{"tid":2262461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩岸是否準戰爭狀態？戰狼發言人當場當機：找不到Q&A","createTime":"2020-10-29T06:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T15:37:16.000Z","uid":337052,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d9946073fb1036fb3f78e8b771fbabeb60280ebc","tid":2262461,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:50:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">被問兩岸戰爭 中共發言人腦袋卡30秒 他笑 : 機器人當機了!</span></strong><br />\n新頭殼newtalk | 劉于緁 綜合報導<br />\n發布 2020.10.28 | 18:58<br />\n     <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/486/5f99448d800c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F486%2F5f99448d800c8.jpg&h=674f49d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮臉色尷尬，不知所措的樣貌。   圖：翻攝今日海峽臉書<br />\n<br />\n文化大學社科院院長趙建民直言兩岸已經進入「準戰爭狀態」。對此，<span class=\"red\">中國國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮今（28）日被問，整記者問到時，竟「當機」超過三十秒，甚至尷尬笑說 :「先問下個問題好不好」</span>。而民進黨立委王定宇直呼，中共的發言人通通是機器人，不只沒有自己的腦，亂講話還會直接掉腦袋。<br />\n<br />\n對於兩岸是否進入準戰爭狀態，一向砲火猛烈、措辭強硬的中國國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮今天竟然語塞並迅速低頭不斷翻閱手中資料，記者會陷入長達30秒的沉默。<br />\n<br />\n王定宇表示，會發生這樣的事情，原因就是<span class=\"red\">「中共的發言人通通是機器人，沒有自己的腦，上面不給授權、不給資料，就不會講話，因為亂講的後果，不只沒腦，會直接掉腦袋」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n此外，王定宇分析，這也讓外界發現，<span class=\"red\">中共高層根本沒有將「準戰爭狀態」列入問答題庫，更遑論進入「戰爭狀態」</span>，所以發言人無法立即反應。<br />\n<br />\n王定宇更幽默表示，今天這個事件，唯一該擔心的是沒有按照預定內容提問的「記者」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-28/485997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-10-28%2F485997&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KisIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=57d5c73c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-10-28/485997</a>"},{"pid":"d7c8011de709fe182052a3484e283fff8b915b30","tid":2262461,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h6cY-NZCylQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh6cY-NZCylQ&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KisIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=0930ad57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h6cY-NZCylQ</a><br />\n被問&quot;準戰爭狀態&quot;? 國台辦發言人罕見語塞"},{"pid":"ababb815aeda6e8dc2d0f6ff20538c33367c45b9","tid":2262461,"uid":160592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"又要換人了<br />\n立堅定春螢"},{"pid":"995836f08d9adf56b439d6da62e077ca50003279","tid":2262461,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rULGGxxL1Dc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrULGGxxL1Dc&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KisIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=d7dce5b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rULGGxxL1Dc</a><br />\n國台辦被問兩岸進入準戰爭狀態語塞 綠諷「讀稿機當機」"},{"pid":"f01480beaeebcb505076439423fa0255150a7d5c","tid":2262461,"uid":59522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"吓？打？我&hellip;我無諗住打架喎&hellip;<br />\n我諗住靠口交部架炸"},{"pid":"8f06b3fbe77172faaca6e2b6f1975fa018fd9f36","tid":2262461,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ababb815aeda6e8dc2d0f6ff20538c33367c45b9","tid":2262461,"uid":160592,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"又要換人了<br />\n立堅定春螢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:55:14.000Z","msg":"朱鳳蓮是小戰狼<br />\n比不上爽春堅"},{"pid":"ad5866ad5452ef6410ef5c614cde669bb7877199","tid":2262461,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:55:43.000Z","msg":"弱撚智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d4539afad05af8ed698889f73f142b8750d99b","tid":2262461,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"其實而家兩岸區隔本身都已經係戰爭狀態"},{"pid":"b6d0139bb941ae566cd7bcd6de61720d199d81df","tid":2262461,"uid":337052,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"43d4539afad05af8ed698889f73f142b8750d99b","tid":2262461,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"